These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, drama, family
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
4 different games are played: domino, whist, backgammon, canasta
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the australian and the person watching epic movies##2
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | drama      | disaster      | family    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| Game     | whist    | canasta       | backgammon     | domino     |

