.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, weightlifting, sailing
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, polish, canadian, german
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the german is on the far left##1
5. the german is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
6. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Sport          | snowboarding     | sailing     | rowing       | weightlifting    |
| Hobby         | photography | singing   | card-games | woodworking |
| Nationality   | german    | canadian | polish    | russian        |

