.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, sudoku, cooking, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, spinach, grapes, apricot
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
8. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby      | gardening | sudoku  | cooking    | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Food         | spinach    | apricot | zucchini | grapes  |

