.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, broccoli, kiwi, pineapple
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, musician, entrepreneur, electrician
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the musician and the person eating avocado##2
2. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the musician##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking sprite is the person eating pineapple##1
6. the musician is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the dressmaker##1
8. the electrician is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | kiwi   | avocado     | broccoli | pineapple |
| Job   | entrepreneur | electrician | dressmaker   | musician     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | almond-milk      | lemonade     | sprite       |

