.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, pakistani, russian
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, blue, emerald, turquise
1. the argentine is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the dutch##3
3. the lawyer is the person who likes lilac##1
4. the architect is between the pakistani and the dutch##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the russian##1
7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the russian##3
8. the pakistani is the person who likes emerald##1
9. the dutch is on the left or right of the russian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality          | pakistani      | russian | dutch      | argentine |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Color   | emerald    | turquise   | blue     | lilac   |

