.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, coral, ivory, yellow
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, daffodil, aconite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Color           | lavender    | coral   | ivory | yellow |
| Flower   | iris     | daffodil   | aconite         | marigold        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

