.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
City: hannover, hamburg, marseilles, london
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, aconite, marigold
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 3. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| City         | marseilles    | hannover  | hamburg | london   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Flower   | marigold      | aconite | orchid | rose  |

