.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, pony, chinchilla
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, paramedic, police-officer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the paramedic is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the teacher is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
8. the police-officer is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Pet          | pony | horse    | chinchilla | bird    |
| Job         | police-officer     | teacher | paramedic  | designer |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

