.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, blend, davidoff
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, rowing, soccer
1. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| Cigar           | pall-mall    | davidoff | blend     | prince |
| Sport   | climbing | rowing    | handball | soccer    |

