.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, nectarine, raspberry
House: futuristic, modern, victorian, palace
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, may, february
1. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
5. the palace house is the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the modern house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food          | garlic   | nectarine | cauliflower | raspberry |
| House   | victorian   | modern     | futuristic      | palace  |
| Birthday   | march | august   | may    | february   |

