4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
7. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating mango##1
8. the person eating mango is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
