The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, daffodil, amaryllis
City: hamburg, miami, london, marseilles
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
6. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to miami and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsbegonia##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Flower         | begonia | daffodil    | sunflower      | amaryllis |
