.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, mah-jongg, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding, surfing, badminton
1. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person playing poker##1
9. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game    | scrabble      | poker | whist       | mah-jongg  |
| Hobby       | woodworking | board-games | writing    | traveling |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | biathlon         | surfing | badminton     |

