.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, lettuce, raspberry
House: victorian, farmhouse, colonial, wooden
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, country, classical
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the victorian house##1
3. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the fan of classical##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | raspberry          | lettuce     | avocado   | cabbage   |
| House           | wooden | victorian | farmhouse | colonial |
| Music-Genre   | reggae          | classical | country   | hip-hop |

