.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, boat, subway, bike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, classical, rock, r&b
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, snake, turtle
1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
2. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the turtle is between the person driving the bike and the fan of r&b##2
5. the person driving the bike is the fan of indie##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Transport           | boat | tram | subway | bike      |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | r&b | classical       | indie  |
| Pet           | rat          | snake  | turtle       | guinea-pig |

