.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, september, april, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, musical, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, snowmobile, tram
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Birthday    | april   | august    | september      | october |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy  | zombie | superhero | musical     |
| Transport   | scooter | ship        | snowmobile  | tram        |

