3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of jazz is between the person who's birthday is in september and the fan of gospel##2
6. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
