.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, blueberry, cranberry, plum
House: modern, craftsman, cape-cod, wooden
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, go, monopoly
1. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the modern house##1
3. the person playing go is the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person playing billiard is between the person eating avocado and the person eating cranberry##2
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
7. the person playing go is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cranberry | blueberry  | avocado  | plum           |
| House     | modern | cape-cod | craftsman   | wooden |
| Game   | monopoly   | billiard       | domino | go  |

 